Entertainer Zodwa Wabantu called off her wedding and is determined to get at least half of her lobola money back. Read: ZODWA CALLS OFF WEDDING AGAIN! Speaking to Drum, Zodwa says that she needs to discuss a way forward with her ex-fiancé since the wedding is officially off. Zodwa revealed to the magazine that Ntobeko’s family would have to give her back at least half the lobola money."We will have to split the lobola money in half. It’s only fair" she said. A while back, the controversial dancer announced that they have split, suggesting that her rise to fame may have been a factor in the breakup and now says that she will never get back together with Ntobeko ever. Zodwa also adds that she will be wearing her wedding dress on the last episode of her reality show. 